Package it.polimi.ingsw.messages.request

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RequestGameEnd
    Sent by the server when the game ends, makes the client display the game end message
    RequestGameInformation
    Sent by the server, gives the client all the lobby information
    RequestKillPlayer
    Sent by the server when a player loses and must by deleted from the game.
    RequestPing
    Ping from the server
    RequestPlayerGod
    Server asks client to pick a god
    RequestPowerCoordinates
    Server asks client for coordinates to execute a turn step
    RequestServerInformation
    Server send lobby info to the client
    RequestUpdateBoardView
    Server tells the client to updated the board
    RequestWaitOpponentMove
    Server makes client wait for opponent's move
    RequestWorkerPlacement
    Server asks client to select two tiles for their workers
